<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Customized Flight Offers</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            color: #333;
        }
        .offer {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }
        .offer h2 {
            color: #555;
            margin-top: 0;
        }
        .offer p {
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Customized Flight Offers</h1>

        <div class="offer">
            <h2>Exclusive Offer for You!</h2>
            <p>Based on your previous travels, we have a special discount offer:</p>
            <p><strong>Destination:</strong> Paris</p>
            <p><strong>Discount:</strong> 20% off on round-trip flights to Paris!</p>
            <p><strong>Promo Code:</strong> PARIS20</p>
            <p>Hurry up and book now!</p>
        </div>

        <div class="offer">
            <h2>Popular Destinations</h2>
            <p>Here are some popular destinations you might be interested in:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>New York:</strong> Explore the Big Apple with discounted flights!</li>
                <li><strong>London:</strong> Enjoy a trip to London with great deals on flights!</li>
                <li><strong>Tokyo:</strong> Discover the vibrant city of Tokyo with exclusive discounts!</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="offer">
            <h2>Flash Sale!</h2>
            <p>Don't miss our limited-time flash sale:</p>
            <p><strong>Destination:</strong> Rome</p>
            <p><strong>Discount:</strong> 30% off on all flights to Rome!</p>
            <p><strong>Promo Code:</strong> ROME30</p>
            <p>Book now before it's too late!</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
